@startuml
[*] --> Idle

Idle --> DoorOpen : Door Opened
DoorOpen --> Idle : Door Closed

Idle --> ReadyToCook : Set Time/Power
ReadyToCook --> Cooking : Start

Cooking --> Stopped : Door Opened
Cooking --> Stopped : Cancel

Stopped --> Idle : Next Use
Stopped --> [*] : End

After fixing the syntax issues by replacing colons with caret symbols and parentheses:

[*] --> Idle

Idle --> DoorOpen ^ (Door Opened)
DoorOpen --> Idle ^ (Door Closed)

Idle --> ReadyToCook ^ (Set Time/Power)
ReadyToCook --> Cooking ^ (Start)

Cooking --> Stopped ^ (Door Opened)
Cooking --> Stopped ^ (Cancel)

Stopped --> Idle ^ (Next Use)
Stopped --> [*] ^ (End)
@enduml
